HEADWORD: Melodramatic
<hw>Mel`o*dra*mat"ic</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[Cf. F.
<ets>m⟦eacute⟧lodramatique</ets>.]</ety> <def>Of or pertaining to
